So, will Lewis Hamilton be Happy after Sunday’s Formula One season finale in Abu Dhabi?

The Briton, who must finish second to guarantee the title, was, despite the semi-smiles and waves to the crowd, somewhat downbeat after Nico Rosberg stormed to pole in qualifying.

Hamilton was unable to match the supremacy of his Mercedes team-mate, but will take some comfort from the fact he starts directly alongside his rival for tomorrow’s race.

